{{unref}}'''Chivatos''' is a Cuban term for those who cooperated with [[Fulgencio Batista|Batista]]'s Government denouncing people as revolutuionaries or against the regime. Those people had a good salary for do it and the most of them were arrested or executed when the [[Cuban Revolution|Revolution]] triumphed on [[January 1]] of [[1959]].

